message: Wrong lexicographical order for 'java.io.IOException' import. Should be before 'org.junit.Test'.
Wrong lexicographical order for 'java.util.List' import. Should be before 'org.junit.Test'.
Abbreviation in name 'CSVParserTest' must contain no more than '2' consecutive capital letters.
'}' at column 7 should be on the same line as the next part of a multi-block statement (one that directly contains multiple blocks: if/else-if/else, do/while or try/catch/finally).
WhitespaceAround: 'catch' is not followed by whitespace. Empty blocks may only be represented as {} when not part of a multi-block statement (4.1.3)
WhitespaceAround: '{' is not followed by whitespace. Empty blocks may only be represented as {} when not part of a multi-block statement (4.1.3)
WhitespaceAround: '}' is not preceded with whitespace.
